issue.title: Which branch to use for August submission?

content.raw:
baila, answers below…

1\. Which branch to use for August submission?

`tunnel_circuit branch`

2\. Which .ign file to be used for final testing during our unit testing simulation?

`ign launch -v 4 tunnel_circuit_practice.ign worldName:=tunnel_circuit_practice_01`

`ign launch -v 4 tunnel_circuit_practice.ign worldName:=tunnel_circuit_practice_02`

`ign launch -v 4 tunnel_circuit_practice.ign worldName:=tunnel_circuit_practice_03`
